Do the imports really matter?
That's a longer list than I expected. Ok, well let's see if they're _really_ needed by providing no-op implementations:

      const module = await WebAssembly.instantiate(await fs.promises.readFile("./dot2svg.wasm"), {
          wasi_snapshot_preview1: {
